{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Do you have the fastest hand in the West?</strong><br>Step into the dusty streets and face off against the Outlaw in this wild, Western standoff! As you take down Outlaws, they get quicker\u2014can you keep up? But watch your aim, cowboy, because if you shoot the town\u2019s sweet old lady, Miss Abigail... let's just say it won\u2019t end well.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Outlaw Standoff</strong> is an action-packed test of your reflexes. Earn high scores, unlock achievements, and see how long you can survive before the Outlaw outguns you. Just remember: it's you, the Outlaw, and Miss Abigail... and only one of you should get hit!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Features</strong>:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Fast-paced standoffs</strong> with randomized Outlaw appearances.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Progressive difficulty</strong>: The better you do, the quicker the Outlaws get.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Steam Achievements</strong> to unlock and brag about.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Highscore tracking</strong>: Aim to be the quickest hand in the West!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And of course, <strong>don\u2019t shoot Miss Abigail</strong>. She\u2019s too sweet for that.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Blood","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3266240/aa3ad113f24c394b10cf93d6191141da069ae090.jpg"},{"name":"They See Me Rollin","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3266240/63db5e4148b0f3b71debff47ef98653eb699a4c7.jpg"},{"name":"Have You Not Heard?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3266240/684bfd9eb92c6152108325a15d559027abdc7a68.jpg"},{"name":"Unintended Conseque